WEBVTT

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:30.616
Negaki doirada hech qanday markaz bo'lmasa

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:33.176
uning ichki yoki tashqi xalqasi yo’q,

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:36.096
boshqalardan ko’proq yo kamroq 
mehrga arziydigan

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.320
hech kim bo’lmaydi.

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:41.416
Bu g’ayritabiiy altruistni oddiy

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:42.680
insondan ajratib turadi.

00:09:43.400 --> 00:09:46.976
Bu ko’pchilik, balki aksariyat insonlar

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:48.976
erishsa bo'ladigan dunyo manzarasidir.

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:51.256
Chunki altruizm va odamiylik 
xislati jamiyat

00:09:51.280 --> 00:09:55.000
doirasida allaqchon har yerda 
yuz bermoqda.

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:58.376
Psixolog Stiven Pinker va 
boshqalar fikricha

00:09:58.400 --> 00:10:01.656
sayyoramiz aholisi o’zlarining 
hamisha kengayuvchi doirasidagi